        ],
        [
          "You've been Germ for so long you can't remember your real name. A cruel childhood nickname became your name in the Warrens is now your pack name. As one might assume with the nickname 'Germ', growing up wasn't exactly easy for you. Your parents had better things to do than be parents, and you were fairly isolated as a child and teen. It's only after being scooped up in a shovel party and getting jumped into the Nosferatu that you first found a true sense of belonging. These were your brothers and sisters in Caine. Not even Caine. The bonds of clan reached out across sect, that's how much family meant to you and yours.Disfigurement seemed a small price to pay. Until Warwick betrayed the clan, selling out the Sabbat Nosferatu. You lost allies, good Nosferatu, during the retaking of Atlanta. Thus did you realize the truth of vampire hypocrisy. The clan ties you were brought up to value meant nothing in the end. So you rejected your clan. You actively sought out Joseph Pander, and had him strip away everything about you that was Nosferatu. You haven't bothered to inform your former clan of this, though - why give up a perfectly good schrecknet login? Now you work for the good of the Pander faction."
